<td valign="top" width="82">Tick Size</td>
<td valign="top" width="234">0.25 Paise or in Rupee terms INR 0.0025</td>
<td valign="top" width="163"></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top" width="82">Trading Hours</td>
<td valign="top" width="234">Monday to Friday between 9:00 AM to 5:00 PM</td>
<td valign="top" width="163"></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top" width="82">Expiry Cycle</td>
<td valign="top" width="234">Upto 12 month contracts</td>
