<td valign="top" width="82">Last trading day</td>
<td valign="top" width="234">Contracts trade till 12:30 PM, 2 days before the last working day.</td>
<td valign="top" width="163">Equity derivatives continue to trade till 3:30 PM of the expiry day.</td>
</tr>
